plugin: manual
name: input/mouse
requires: device.category == 'MOUSE'
_description:
 PURPOSE:
     This test will test your mouse device
 STEPS:
     1. Move the mouse
     2. Perform some single/double/right click operations
 VERIFICATION:
     Did the mouse work as expected??

plugin: manual
name: input/keyboard
command: keyboard_test
requires: device.category == 'KEYBOARD'
_description:
 PURPOSE:
     This test will test your keyboard
 STEPS:
     1. Click on Test
     2. On the open text area, use your keyboard to type something
 VERIFICATION:
     Is your keyboard working properly?
